lead_paragraph: Manchester United do not need to practise their finishing to improve their goal-scoring record ahead of Sunday's Premier League game at Everton, manager Jose Mourinho said.

headline.print_headline: Man United Not Putting in Extra Work on Finishing-Mourinho
